Package de.lambeck.pned.elements.gui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGuiArc
    Sub type of IArc for arcs in a IGuiModel.
    IGuiElement
    Sub type of IElement for elements in a IGuiModel.
    IGuiNode
    Sub type of INode for nodes in a IGuiModel.
    IGuiPlace
    Sub type of IGuiNode for places in a IGuiModel (places with a "token" circle).
    IGuiTransition
    Interface for transitions in a IGuiModel.
    IHasZValue
    Interface for elements with a z-value (height) level
    ISelectable
    Interface for elements that can be selected.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GuiArc
    Implements the arcs (arrows) of the Petri net.
    GuiElement
    Superclass GuiElement implements the common members for all elements.
    GuiNode
    Superclass GuiNode implements the common members for all nodes.
    GuiPlace
    Implements the places for the GUI model of the Petri net.
    GuiTransition
    Implements the transitions for the GUI model of the Petri net.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EArcDirection
    Possible directions for arcs to be used to calculate the arcAnchor in IGuiTransition.
